articles.title: Man and daughter found dead in Sengkang flat after unit below reported bodily fluids dripping from ceiling
articles.content: The deceased were father and daughter, according to a Shin Min Daily News report. The deaths were discovered after an elderly neighbour living in the unit below noticed liquid dripping from her ceiling on Monday morning, reported Shin Min.
